The paper discusses active cyber defense, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR). The study involves investigating optimal control and Nash equilibria, which are topics related to game theory (cs.GT) and control systems (cs.SY). The use of benign worms to combat malicious worms also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Finally, the study involves network security (cs.NI) as the worms spread over the network. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR, followed by cs.GT, cs.SY, cs.AI, and cs.NI.
